404
00:44:00,056 --> 00:44:01,967
Guarnere, close that flap.

405
00:44:02,225 --> 00:44:05,137
Let the Krauts cook
their own goddamn food.

406
00:44:05,812 --> 00:44:07,643
-How we doing, Malark?
-Good.

407
00:44:07,897 --> 00:44:08,886
-Good?
-Yeah.

408
00:44:09,107 --> 00:44:11,382
