419
00:45:06,831 --> 00:45:09,425
lt's been a day of firsts.

420
00:45:15,256 --> 00:45:17,087
Don't you think, Guarnere?

421
00:45:20,345 --> 00:45:22,654
Yes, sir.

422
00:45:24,641 --> 00:45:25,710
Carry on.

423
00:45:25,934 --> 00:45:27,572
-Night, sir.
